text: Estuaire is the most populous province in Gabon. The provincial capital is Libreville, which is also Gabon's national capital. == Departments == There are five departments: * Komo Department (Kango) * Komo-Mondah Department (Ntoum) * Komo-Oc√©an Department (Ndzomoe) * Noya Department (Cocobeach) * Libreville (department and capital city) == References == Category:Provinces of Gabon
